&lt;P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"&gt;&lt;FONT class=bodytextspaced&gt;Ratio of money spent on training: total vs. maintenance?&lt;BR&gt;&lt;SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"&gt;&lt;FONT class=bodytextspaced&gt;Every organization spends a certain amount of money on continuing education (such as training conferences) for their employees.&lt;SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;100:1 would mean that the organization spends a total of $100 on training of which maintenance gets only $1 for training.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; mso-list: l15 level1 lfo10; tab-stops: list .5in"&gt;&lt;FONT class=bodytextspaced&gt;&lt;SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol"&gt;&lt;SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore"&gt;&lt;SPAN style="FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;100:1&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
