&lt;P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"&gt;&lt;FONT class=bodytextspaced&gt;How often does this happen?&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"&gt;&lt;FONT class=bodytextspaced&gt;A machine (asset) is down and the part(s) needed to fix it is unavailable.&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
