&lt;LI class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-list: l23 level1 lfo26; tab-stops: list .5in"&gt;&lt;FONT class=bodytextspaced&gt;How did you justify your CMMS?&lt;/FONT&gt; 
